ants":[{"name":"Rodger","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Roger  , in part from the surname derived from the given name in the Middle Ages."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Roger De Thourotte was born about 1050, in Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France. He married Alix de Montmorency in 1090. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"Abt 1050–":"umbes 1050–Surnud","1063–1129":"1063–1129","1083–1142":"1083–1142","1050–Male":"1050–Surnud","1129":"1129","1090":"1090","1142":"1142","1063":"1063","Abt 1050":"umbes 1050","1083":"1083","1050":"1050","Thourotte, Oise, Picardy, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"Abt 1050–":"noin 1050–Kuollut","1063–1129":"1063–1129","1083–1142":"1083–1142","1050–Male":"1050–Kuollut","1129":"1129","1090":"1090","1142":"1142","1063":"1063","Abt 1050":"noin 1050","1083":"1083","1050":"1050","Thourotte, Oise, Picardy, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, Ranska","Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, Ranska"},"fr":{"Abt 1050–":"environ 1050–Décédé","1063–1129":"1063–1129","1083–1142":"1083–1142","1050–Male":"1050–Décédé","1129":"1129","1090":"1090","1142":"1142","1063":"1063","Abt 1050":"environ 1050","1083":"1083","1050":"1050","Thourotte, Oise, Picardy, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France","Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France","lifeSummary":"Roger De Thourotte est né environ 1050, à Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France. Il a épousé Alix de Montmorency en 1090. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"Abt 1050–":"um 1050–Verstorben","1063–1129":"1063–1129","1083–1142":"1083–1142","1050–Male":"1050–Verstorben","1129":"1129","1090":"1090","1142":"1142","1063":"1063","Abt 1050":"um 1050","1083":"1083","1050":"1050","Thourotte, Oise, Picardy, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, Frankreich","Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, France":"Thourotte, Oise, Picardie, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Roger De Thourotte wu